{"tid":842825,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普巴已告知隊友，若有必要，他會表明不再為摩帥出場比賽","createTime":"2018-09-30T15:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T01:35:05.000Z","uid":124292,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3b3c0e68fa4189b0451066947015eb63fb90d873","tid":842825,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"著名記者Duncan Casltes在《每日鏡報》撰寫了報道，其中他透露，根據在曼聯隊中的消息源，普巴已經告知隊友們，他不會在和主帥摩連奴的鬥爭中屈服。若雙方的矛盾加重，在有必要時，普巴甚至已經準備好要「抗爭到底」，公開表明不再願意為摩連奴效力的立場。<br />\n<br />\nCastles還透露，普巴和摩連奴的關係已經經歷了一系列的考驗。2017-18賽季前半段，普巴受了嚴重的腳筋傷勢，曼聯的工作人員認為這是他聘請私人體能教練所導致的。在上賽季後半段，普巴和他的經理人拉奧拿都希望摩連奴能改變他的戰術，讓普巴從防守責任中解脫出來。拉奧拿也向歐洲幾家大俱樂部兜售了普巴，其中就包括曼聯的對手曼城。"},{"pid":"aa3e905d8d62d63bc64f1cf41c466dc092d97b96","tid":842825,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/paul-pogba-tells-manchester-united-13334169.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fnews%2Fpaul-pogba-tells-manchester-united-13334169.amp&d=4ehNFi2R%2FwCFrCvLfGYmRzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=28739222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/paul-pogba-tells-manchester-united-13334169.amp</a>"},{"pid":"01effd4a3a3c2e294de3e13ea9e857d120b3e94f","tid":842825,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0b1c20a473403df91f94b3dd596807ff77bb7e","tid":842825,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:40:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3ffca1bc7691b608126811cc59324083f34beb0","tid":842825,"uid":53629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:44:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7f8c0926861572cb16659a2ecfd52697d8d4e1e","tid":842825,"uid":33601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep